=======================================
ğŸ§ª Sample API Usage
=======================================

GET all todos:
--------------
GET https://dummyjson.com/todos

POST a new task:
----------------
POST https://dummyjson.com/todos/add
Body:
{
  "todo": "Do the dishes",
  "completed": false,
  "userId": 1
}

PUT update a task:
------------------
PUT https://dummyjson.com/todos/1
Body:
{
  "completed": true
}

DELETE a task:
--------------
DELETE https://dummyjson.com/todos/1

